eheh extension replaces your default tab with a variety of useful features, including:

— Live Stream Recommendations: Access live streams from popular platforms like Twitch, YouTube, Facebook, and Kick. The extension automatically displays your favorite streamers based on your viewing history. You can also browse thousands of streams by game or platform without visiting multiple websites. Everything can be done directly within your default tab;

— Link Recommendation System: Get suggestions for links that may interest you at the moment, based on your browsing history. The extension scrapes some websites you visit and suggests links, such as extracting YouTube's homepage and recommended videos, then displaying them in your default tab. The improved bookmark system allows you to save your favorite websites for quick access and discover hundreds of popular sites, sorted by categories such as News, Social Media, Sports, Shopping, Games, Finance, Science & Education, and Lifestyle & Health;

— Reddit Client: Quickly read the latest posts from Reddit using the built-in client. You can also add and manage your favorite subreddits;

— Gmail Notifications: Receive notifications for new emails along with previews, so you stay updated without constantly checking your inbox;

— Sports Notifications: Stay informed about your favorite sports teams and leagues by subscribing to receive notifications for upcoming games. Never miss an important event;

— Quick Google Search: Start a Google search directly from the main screen of the tab by simply typing your query;

— Curated YouTube Video List: Browse a curated selection of YouTube videos, organized by categories for easy access;

— Access to Chatbots: Quickly connect with chatbots like ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, Mistral, and Poe for immediate assistance;

— Built-in Music Player: Enjoy a built-in Spotify music player and features for discovering new films, TV shows, and music;

— Market Data Aggregation: Stay updated with information on stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, indices, and overall economic markets;

— Easy Access to Google Services: Quickly navigate to essential Google services, such as Maps, Docs, Calendar, News, Translate, Drive, and more;

— Stress Relief Sounds: Use the built-in clicking sounds feature designed to help relieve stress while browsing;

— Multiple Color Themes: Personalize your browsing experience with various color themes to choose from;

